+ * Qualcomm sensor registry property interface
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2026 The HexagonRPC Contributors
+ *
+ * This file is part of HexagonRPC.
+ *
+ * HexagonRPC is free software: you can redistribute it and/or modify
